title: Added semantic ui syntactic sugar for: form, fields, field and rexport for HTML label tab.
body:
Save keystrokes when creating Semantic UI forms:

```
    uiform(
      uifield(
        label('Start date'),
        shiny_text_input('visitors_from', tags$input(type = 'date'), value = '01-01-1980')
      ),
      uifield(
        label('End date'),
        shiny_text_input('visitors_to', tags$input(type = 'date'), value = as.character(today()))
      )
    )
```

title: Mateusz uimenu
body:
_uimenu_ creates a menu using a helper function _menuItem_. 

_menuItem_ creates one menu item/tab which is then added to the menu by _uimenu_

TODO: Check which features of a menu item are still missing implementation: dropdown, search, other (?)
TODO: Static item should be more flexible (not necessarily "header")
TODO: Submenus (e.g. in a vertical menu)
